      "writtenOn": "2017-04-17T23:07:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "alignof(T), right?\n\nThe idea for this bytes-allocated is to track how many bytes we cost, not so much how many we\u0027ve used.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 61,
        "startChar": 41,
        "endLine": 61,
        "endChar": 49
      },
      "revId": "a5b576058f61184ef84347bfa821bf663b7a19d2",
